{
  "message": "feat(web): add service logos and security docs page\n\n- Add SVG logos for services: Tailscale, Anthropic, OpenAI, Google,\n  GitHub, Cloudflare, Supabase, Vercel\n- Add security documentation page at /docs/security\n\nPart of Accounts & Connections wizard step (4ey).\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
